original_text: Which was the son of Aminadab, which was the son of Aram, which was the son of Esrom, which was the son of Phares, which was the son of Juda,
korean_text: 그 위는 아미나답이요 그 위는 아니요 그 위는 헤스론이요 그 위는 베레스요 그 위는 유다요

sentences.original_text: Which was the son of Aminadab
which was the son of Aram
which was the son of Esrom
which was the son of Phares
which was the son of Juda
